OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMisty with some fog and drizzle
OL,6,Fslowly lifting, allowing brighter
OL,7,Fspells during the afternoon and
OL,8,Ffeeling milder. Mist and fog could
OL,9,Flinger near eastern coasts. Increasing
OL,10,Fchance of showers during Monday
OL,11,Fafternoon.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FTurning drier for a time
OL,14,FMonday evening with variable cloud
OL,15,Famounts. A few showers or some rain
OL,16,Fmight return as cloud increases and
OL,17,Fthickens again overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
