OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FTurning breezier Tuesday,
OL,6,Fafter a cloudy morning with showery
OL,7,Frain. Rain dying out and clearing east
OL,8,Fin the afternoon with cloud breaking
OL,9,Fto allow some bright or sunny spells.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,12,FWednesday, morning rain clearing, then
OL,13,Fcolder, brighter and turning mostly
OL,14,Fdry. Thursday, windy and bright with
OL,15,Fthickening cloud later. Friday less
OL,16,Fwindy with sunshine and showers.
OL,17,FTemperatures near normal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
